platform/chrome: cros_ec_sysfs: Add cold-ap-off to sysfs reboot.

Add cold-ap-off to ChromeOS EC sysfs reboot file option, corresponds to
the EC_REBOOT_COLD_AP_OFF flag, that will reset EC and keep AP off.

